<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="56" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1047,1252]" pageId="1" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,313,1084,1108]" pageId="1" pageNumber="56">Remarks.</emphasis>
The cuticular pattern was identical to 
<taxonomicName box="[764,907,1084,1108]" class="Heterotardigrada" family="Echiniscidae" genus="Echiniscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Echiniscoidea" pageId="1" pageNumber="56" phylum="Tardigrada" rank="species" species="perviridis">
<emphasis box="[764,907,1084,1108]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="56">E. perviridis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, though one cirrus A was bifurcated, and the measurements slightly shorter for cephalic papilla, clava, and claws IV than previously reported. Obviously, more specimens are needed from Hubei for a positive identification. This species has been reported from Guizhou Province (
<bibRefCitation author="Wang" box="[212,408,1191,1216]" pageId="1" pageNumber="56" refString="Wang, H., Wang, L. &amp; Li, X. (2007) Tardigrades from Guizhou Province (China) with description of a new species of genus Doryphoribius (Tardigrada: Hypsibiidae). Zootaxa, 1626, 59 - 67." type="journal article" year="2007">
Wang 
<emphasis box="[285,341,1192,1216]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="56">et al.</emphasis>
<number box="[348,408,1191,1215]" pageId="1" pageNumber="56" value="2007.0">2007</number>
</bibRefCitation>
), 
<collectingCountry box="[428,510,1191,1215]" name="Taiwan" pageId="1" pageNumber="56">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Li" box="[524,678,1191,1215]" pageId="1" pageNumber="56" refString="Li, X. &amp; Li, H. (2008) Tardigrades from Taiwan, with the description of a new species of Doryphoribius (Tardigrada, Hypsibiidae). Zoological Science, 25, 554 - 559." type="journal article" year="2008">
Li &amp; Li 
<number box="[618,678,1191,1215]" pageId="1" pageNumber="56" value="2008.0">2008</number>
</bibRefCitation>
), and Hainan Island (
<bibRefCitation author="Li" box="[916,1072,1191,1216]" pageId="1" pageNumber="56" refString="Li, X. &amp; Li, H. (2008) Tardigrades from Taiwan, with the description of a new species of Doryphoribius (Tardigrada, Hypsibiidae). Zoological Science, 25, 554 - 559." type="journal article" year="2008">
Li 
<emphasis box="[949,1005,1192,1216]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="56">et al.</emphasis>
<number box="[1012,1072,1191,1215]" pageId="1" pageNumber="56" value="2008.0">2008</number>
</bibRefCitation>
), but this would be a new record for Hubei Province.
</paragraph>
